1–3: 
<emphasis id="B94932355F42FFA5FDD971461BC6451E" bold="true" box="[616,646,1873,1896]" pageId="2" pageNumber="41">(1)</emphasis>
habitus (dorsolateral view); 
<emphasis id="B94932355F42FFA5FC0171461A8D451E" bold="true" box="[944,973,1873,1896]" pageId="2" pageNumber="41">(2)</emphasis>
